        {
          "_tags": [
            "Theme"
          ],
          "_name": "testimonials1",
          "_styles": {
            ".card-block P": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "font-size": "36px"
            },
            ".card-footer > div": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".card-footer > small": {
              "color": "#553982"
            },
            ".card-block": {
              "font-family": "'Quicksand', sans-serif",
              "googleLink": "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Quicksand:300,400,500,700"
            }
          },
          "testimonial": [
            {
              "text": "“I have worked with Louisa on a number of projects, where she's always displayed professionalism, ability to solve problems quickly and without fuss, adaptability and patience when working with people &amp; equipment.”<div>&nbsp;</div>",
              "media": {
                "image": {
                  "src": "@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-160x106.jpg",
                  "class": "img-circle",
                  "height": 160,
                  "width": 160,
                  "active": true,
                  "link": "",
                  "alt": "",
                  "title": "",
                  "linkInNewWindow": false
                }
              },
              "authorName": "Sarah Fronckevic",
              "authorBio": "<br>Writer/Director/Producer - <br>C'est La Vie, The Investigation"
            },
            {
              "text": "\"As a first-time director, working with Louisa was amazing. She brought the zen and order to my creative chaos, serving as an ideal partnership.\"",
              "media": {
                "image": {
                  "src": "@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/face1.jpg",
                  "class": "img-circle",
                  "height": 160,
                  "width": 160,
                  "active": true
                }
              },
              "authorName": "Shai Hussain",
              "authorBio": "<br>Writer/Director - <br>Three Shades of Brown"
            },
            {
              "text": "“Louisa is a first rate Director and DoP with the ability to generate outstanding ideas that add new dimensions to any scene or film that she is involved in. She came onboard with my film and took the entire production to a completely new level and made it the first rate film that it is. Hard working, committed and full of ability are the best ways to describe her. I would highly recommend anyone to work with her.”",
              "media": {
                "image": {
                  "src": "@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/face2.jpg",
                  "class": "img-circle",
                  "height": 160,
                  "width": 160,
                  "active": true
                }
              },
              "authorName": "Daniel Casper",
              "authorBio": "<br>Writer/Producer - <br>Environmental Enforcement<br>"
            }
          ],
          "_anchor": "testimonials1-j",
          "_params": {
            "showTitle": true,
            "showSubtitle": false,
            "showImages": false,
            "showName": true,
            "showBio": true,
