            "overlayOpacity": 0.5
          },
          "media": {
            "image": {
              "width": 1400,
              "src": "@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/gallery/desktop.jpg"
            },
            "video": {
              "active": true,
              "src": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nBRbjCd0UFE",
              "aspectratio": "16:9",
              "autoplay": false,
              "loop": false
            },
            "iconFont": {
              "class": "mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-msg-box4",
              "link": "",
              "size": 250
            }
          },
          "title": "CORPORATE/DOC WORK",
          "text": "<br>I've worked on a whole range of videos including crowd funding videos, conferences, private events, live recordings, weddings and interviews.<br> <br>My involvement in this work varies from being simply a camera operator to self shooting the whole thing, meaning I directed it, shot it, lit it, recorded the sound, edited and colour graded it.<br> <br>This showreel prodominantly showcases work where I acted as a self shooter but it also includes a few examples from projects where I was just the DoP.",
          "buttons": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">MORE</a>"
        },
        {
          "_inherit": "msg-box5",
          "_tags": [
            "Theme"
          ],
          "_name": "msg-box4",
          "_styles": {
            "H3": {
              "font-size": "25px",
              "text-align": "center"
            },
            "P": {
              "font-size": "15px",
              "text-align": "center"
            }
          },
          "_anchor": "msg-box4-w",
          "_params": {
            "showTitle": true,
            "showText": true,
            "showButtons": false,
            "inverse": true,
            "imageSize": "60",
            "paddingTop": "3",
            "paddingBottom": "2",
            "bgImageRadio": false,
            "bgImage": "@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/jumbotron.jpg",
            "parallax": true,
            "bgColorRadio": true,
            "bgColor": "#ffffff",
            "bgVideoRadio": false,
            "bgVideo": {
              "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw"
            },
            "overlay": true,
            "overlayColor": "#fff",
            "overlayOpacity": 0.5
          },
          "media": {
            "image": {
              "width": 1400,
              "src": "@THEME_PATH@/components/_images/gallery/desktop.jpg"
            },
            "video": {
              "active": true,
              "src": "http://vimeo.com/23311679",
              "aspectratio": "16:9",
              "autoplay": false,
              "loop": false
            },
            "iconFont": {
              "class": "mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-msg-box4",
              "link": "",
              "size": 250
            }
          },
          "title": "CREATIVE DOP WORK",
          "text": "<br>As a DoP I've worked on a lot of projects, with a lot of different cinematography styles, ranging from minimalististly lit documentary style to the harsh but effective horror look.<br> <br>Past projects include multiple feature films, shorts and music videos.<br> <br>Noteworthy past projects include feature film 'Wecome To The Majority' which won the Best Cinematography award at the 2013 Yellow Fever  Independant Film Festival.<br>",
          "buttons": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">MORE</a>"
        },
