          "title": "ABOUT ME",
          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.07rem; line-height: 1.5;\">I'm based in North London and I've been shooting videos and films for over six years now and I absolutely love doing the work that I do. I'm proud of the results I have achieved up to this point but that doesn't mean that I'm done learning, I'm determined to become even better as both a DoP and as a Self-Shooter.</span><br></p>",
          "button": "<a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\">SEE ALL TEMPLATES</a>"
        },
